updates.HtmlString: Fixed Collector Booster: Serialized RM Multiverse Legends now appear in slot 1 (VERY rarely).
Fixed Collector Booster: Serialized Praetors now occupt slot 2 instead of 1 (if you've lucky enough to get one).
Fixed Set Booster (again): Now always includes a rare (or mythic!) in slot 2.
Fixed Draft Booster: Now ensures at least one rare per pack.
Fixed Set Booster: Now only includes commander cards num 72-79.
Fixed Set Booster: Fewer mythics. Fixedserialized cards 10x more rare. (Sorry for both! It's more accurate now)
Fixed Draft Booster: Can now have multiple R/M cards (up to 2) in a pack.
